          <p>The current pricing plan is shown on our pricing page <a class="faq-link" href="/pricing">here</a>.</p>
          <a class="top" href="#top">Back to top</a>
        </div>

      <hr>
      <div class="row spacer" id="why_cost">
          <h3 'Source Sans Pro'>Why isn't it free?</h3>
          <p>Sadly there are costs to running any online application. Many of these costs vary with the number of users. To allow us to keep it running, it must at least cover those costs. To keep it simple, effective and friendly to use, we don't want to introduce advertising which gets in the way. We hope that you will agree that it is a reasonable cost and easily covered by the saving in your time. If you run a small business and have to record expenses or if you use Bulldog Clip to reclaim expenses, you could be saving hours of your time each month. If you just want to use Bulldog Clip to just track where your money is going, you will be amazed what insights you can achieve, even if you don't track every last penny. We believe that we will need to charge it every year, not just as a one off payment, because the unavoidable costs of running the system also happen every year.</p>
          <a class="top" href="#top">Back to top</a>
        </div>

