      <div class="row spacer" id="cancel_account">
          <h3 'Source Sans Pro'>How can I cancel my account?</h3>
          <p>You can cancel your account at any point. Log in to Bulldog Clip, select the 'Account' option from the main menu. In the account view select 'Cancel Account'. You will be asked to confirm that you do want to cancel the account. Your account will then be closed. Make sure your export any data you want to keep before cancelling. Your data will be stored for 60 days in case you change your mind. If we don't hear from you with in 60 days your data will be purged.</p>
